.SH NAME
perlcheat \- Perl 5 Cheat Sheet
.SH DESCRIPTION
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This 'cheat sheet' is a handy reference, meant for beginning Perl
programmers. Not everything is mentioned, but 195 features may
already be overwhelming.
.SS "The sheet"
